  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242657.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>鸿海精密董事长郭台铭周三表示，该公司并不急于与陷入困境的日本消费电子产品制造商索尼达成投资协议。</strong>鸿海精密一直在积极扩张制造用 户高清电视机的大屏幕面板业务。作为公司增加面板业务专有技术努力的一部分，该公司已经收购了夏普部分资产，并在与夏普进行谈判，考虑购买后者10%的股 份。不过两家公司目前仍未就收购价格达成一致意见。郭台铭在鸿海精密年度股东大会中表示，“我们希望帮助夏普实现复兴。我认为，夏普将作出明智的决定。”</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dda5447/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242657.htm&amp;t=%E9%B8%BF%E6%B5%B7%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E9%83%AD%E5%8F%B0%E9%93%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E5%A4%8F%E6%99%AE%E8%BE%BE%E6%88%90%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242657.htm&amp;t=%E9%B8%BF%E6%B5%B7%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E9%83%AD%E5%8F%B0%E9%93%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E5%A4%8F%E6%99%AE%E8%BE%BE%E6%88%90%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242657.htm&amp;t=%E9%B8%BF%E6%B5%B7%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E9%83%AD%E5%8F%B0%E9%93%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E5%A4%8F%E6%99%AE%E8%BE%BE%E6%88%90%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242657.htm&amp;t=%E9%B8%BF%E6%B5%B7%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E9%83%AD%E5%8F%B0%E9%93%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E5%A4%8F%E6%99%AE%E8%BE%BE%E6%88%90%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img bord